      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf28c0d337316ecd8cfeb5f"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "He was skeptical about IE since they actually shared little that would actually help the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeriphery],Periphery]] worlds where they conducted expeditions.\n\nThe reports about them weren't assuring either... a motley group of opportunists, spies, and thieves instead of actual scientists that had already been banned on several worlds.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Perhaps they have changed.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
